<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="24Apr1939"><font color="red">24 April 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  your letter of the 20th. I am afraid we had already sent the proof to Prof. Zimmer in Germany &hellip; we will send another to Oxford. </div>
